name: come out and play | Celebrating #Henosy
description: My NFT journey begins 4 months ago on HEN, and it's been such an exciting experience in the middle of COVID-19 pandemic. It encourages me to experimenting and playing with my arts, also discovering many amazing artist. It's such a wonderful community, hope in the future HEN will be better and stronger.  Happy 0.5 years Hicetnunc!
